    "spell": {
        "name": "Animal Feature",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Without fully transforming your body, you gain one animalistic feature, which you select from the list below each time you Cast the Spell. \n* **Cat Eyes** You gain low-light vision.\n* **Claws** You gain a claw attack that deals 1d6 slashing damage and has the agile, finesse, and unarmed traits.\n* **Jaws** You gain a jaws attack that deals 1d8 piercing damage and has the unarmed trait.",
